
<section class="hero">
<div class="container">
<h1>	Mobile APP Development, Online Marketing and Website Design with Amazing Results</h1>
<p class="main tagline">We are a professional digital marketing agency passionate about providing the market with all-in-one, innovative and result focused solutions for any thriving, ambitious businesses – from individual freelancing companies to established corporations. </p>

<a class="signup button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#something" href="#">Contact us now!</a>
<div class="modal fade" id="something" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="somethingLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
